    <item>
      <title>特朗普针对世界上关税最高的非洲王国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-targets-african-kingdom-with-highest-tariff-in-the-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）对莱索托（Lesotho）的小型南部非洲山王国征收了50％的互惠关税，这是任何主权国家的最高征税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-targets-african-kingdom-with-highest-tariff-in-the-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 08:54:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国关注我们对欧盟对特朗普关税的报复的重要技术</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/france-eyes-us-big-tech-in-eu-retaliation-to-trump-s-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国正在推动欧洲联盟以应对唐纳德·特朗普总统的关税袭击美国科技公司，这将向广大服务部门扩大贸易战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/france-eyes-us-big-tech-in-eu-retaliation-to-trump-s-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 08:34:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟的顶级外交官说，欧洲必须从我们身上多样化。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/europe-must-diversify-defense-from-us-eu-s-top-diplomat-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该集团最高的外交政策官员说，欧洲联盟需要扩大对美国军事设备的依赖，因为它消化了唐纳德·特朗普总统决定以惩罚关税打击贸易伙伴的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/europe-must-diversify-defense-from-us-eu-s-top-diplomat-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 08:08:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>部长说，匈牙利将开始退出ICC的过程。</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/hungary-set-to-start-process-of-exiting-icc-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维克多·奥尔班（Viktor Orban）政府高级官员说，匈牙利将于周四开始法律程序退出国际刑事法院。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/hungary-set-to-start-process-of-exiting-icc-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 08:02:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的互惠关税对印度意味着什么</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-tariffs-on-india-how-is-country-economy-impacted-what-is-modi-doing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[“关税国王。”关税的“大虐待者”。一个“非常高的关税国家”。多年来，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）一再明确表示，他对印度贸易保护主义贸易政策的看法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/trump-tariffs-on-india-how-is-country-economy-impacted-what-is-modi-doing</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 07:04:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国因涉嫌间谍而拘留三个菲律宾人</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/china-detains-three-filipinos-for-alleged-spying-as-ties-fray</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国表示，它拘留了三名涉嫌间谍的菲律宾国民，这一举动可能会进一步构成北京和马尼拉之间的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/china-detains-three-filipinos-for-alleged-spying-as-ties-fray</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 04:58:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>起亚首席执行官在特朗普的关税云美国观点时向欧洲看</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/kia-ceo-looks-to-europe-as-trump-s-tariffs-cloud-us-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[起亚公司的目标是在唐纳德·特朗普总统的汽车关税和反越门政策中销售欧洲更多的电动汽车。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/kia-ceo-looks-to-europe-as-trump-s-tariffs-cloud-us-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 02:55:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本说，特朗普的24％关税令人失望，发誓家庭援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/japan-calls-trump-s-24-tariff-regrettable-pushes-for-exemption</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本总理表示，在美国宣布对美国安全盟友最高的日本征收新税后，特朗普政府最新的关税范围令人失望，并发誓对国内行业的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/japan-calls-trump-s-24-tariff-regrettable-pushes-for-exemption</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 02:37:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国的目标是将贸易部长派往我们讨论关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/south-korea-holds-emergency-meeting-to-cope-with-tariff-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在特朗普政府宣布向美国安全盟友征收最高的关税率之一之后，韩国的临时领导层被置于紧急模式，以保护依靠出口的经济免受贸易危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-03/south-korea-holds-emergency-meeting-to-cope-with-tariff-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Apr 2025 00:10:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>俄罗斯官方德米特里耶夫（Dmitriev）会见华盛顿的特使维特科夫（Witkoff）</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/russian-negotiator-dmitriev-to-meet-envoy-witkoff-in-washington</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位知情人士说，美国特别特使史蒂夫·维托科夫（Steve Witkoff）有望与俄罗斯高级谈判代表基里尔·德米特里耶夫（Kirill Dmitriev）在华盛顿见面，这是一位知情人士说，在唐纳德·特朗普总统对同行弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）表示沮丧之后，努力使紧张局势变得平稳。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/russian-negotiator-dmitriev-to-meet-envoy-witkoff-in-washington</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 16:21:03 GMT</pubDate>
